on\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kfu1665702580321.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kfu1665702580321.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kfu1665702580321.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kfu1665702580321\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      \n                          Dimension\n                        </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies a comma-separated string that defines the position and size of the form window in pixels.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p refsyn\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"A_FORM\",\n            \"MyInstance\",</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>Dimension <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">XPos</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">YPos</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">XSize</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">YSize</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"kfu1665702580321__table_d13022e1_d13023e1_d13024e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kfu1665702580321__table_d13022e1_d13023e1_d13024e1__entry__1\">\n Arguments\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kfu1665702580321__table_d13022e1_d13023e1_d13024e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kfu1665702580321__table_d13022e1_d13023e1_d13024e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">XPos</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kfu1665702580321__table_d13022e1_d13023e1_d13024e1__entry__2\">\n The horizontal window position, relative to the parent window.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kfu1665702580321__table_d13022e1_d13023e1_d13024e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">YPos</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kfu1665702580321__table_d13022e1_d13023e1_d13024e1__entry__2\">\n The vertical window position, relative to the parent window.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kfu1665702580321__table_d13022e1_d13023e1_d13024e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">XSize</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kfu1665702580321__table_d13022e1_d13023e1_d13024e1__entry__2\">\n Width of the window size.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kfu1665702580321__table_d13022e1_d13023e1_d13024e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">YSize</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kfu1665702580321__table_d13022e1_d13023e1_d13024e1__entry__2\">Height of the window. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kfu1665702580321__section_j54_vwv_dxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d344510e156\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kfu1665702580321__p_d111473e1_d111474e1_d111475e1\">You can set the Dimension window property when\n            creating a new instance of a Form component. For example, the following statement starts\n            a display-only form instance that is 235 pixels wide and 400 pixels high:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"kfu1665702580321__pre_t25_wwv_dxb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$1 = $1 + 1\nnewinstance \"MYFORM\", \"MYFORM%%$1\", \"DISPLAY=TRUE;DIMENSION=0,0,235,400\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"kfu1665702580321__note_u25_wwv_dxb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> To have Windows handle positioning, set\n               both<var class=\"keyword varname\">XPos</var>and<var class=\"keyword varname\">YPos</var>to<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> for all\n            forms. When multiple forms are displayed, Windows stacks them in an offset cascade, with\n            each form displayed one position below and to the right of the previous form. If there\n            are very many open forms the stack continues to the bottom of the application window and\n            begins again at top left position.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kfu1665702580321__p_d111476e1_d111477e1_d111478e1\">You can use the\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$windowproperties</span> ProcScript function to get or set the window\n            position and size of a form instance at runtime. In this case, you must explicitly\n            define the properties XPos, YPos, XSize, and YSize rather than defining the dimension\n            property. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bch1665702773514.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bch1665702773514.html\" title=\"Set or return the current window properties of a Form instance.\">$windowproperties</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kfu1665702580321__section_yp2_1xv_dxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d344510e193\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"kfu1665702580321__ul_rtf_dxv_dxb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kfu1665702580321__li_d42845e1_d42846e1_d42847e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"usl1704692305727.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/usl1704692305727.html\" title=\"Form components provide the user interface for Uniface desktop applications. They are always executed on the client system and can be modal (form retains focus until it is closed) or non-modal (users can switch focus to other forms).\">Forms</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614108\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614108\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Dimension Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Dimension Specifies a comma-separated string that defines the position and size of the form window in pixels. newinstance \"A_FORM\", \"MyInstance\", \" Dimension = XPos , YPos , XSize , YSize \" Arguments Description XPos The horizontal window position, relative to the parent window. YPos The vertical window position, relative to the parent window. XSize Width of the window size. YSize Height of the window. Description You can set the Dimension window property when creating a new instance of a Form component. For example, the following statement starts a display-only form instance that is 235 pixels wide and 400 pixels high: $1 = $1 + 1 newinstance \"MYFORM\", \"MYFORM%%$1\", \"DISPLAY=TRUE;DIMENSION=0,0,235,400\" Copy Note: To have Windows handle positioning, set both XPos and YPos to 0 for all forms. When multiple forms are displayed, Windows stacks them in an offset cascade, with each form displayed one position below and to the right of the previous form. If there are very many open forms the stack continues to the bottom of the application window and begins again at top left position. You can use the $windowproperties ProcScript function to get or set the window position and size of a form instance at runtime. In this case, you must explicitly define the properties XPos, YPos, XSize, and YSize rather than defining the dimension property. For more information, see $windowproperties . Applies To Forms Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}